&lt;p&gt;You will own the accounting operations and due to our company’s growth, help in creating and implementing scalable process improvements. You will help define the strategic direction of the team and also have opportunities to help prepare the annual budget, build and analyze the operating model, and have a voice in key financial decisions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
